{{Infobox dungeon |name = Connecting Cave |image = [[File:Connecting Cave.png|250px]] |caption = A map of Connecting Cave. |tokens = 475,000 |location = Between Routes 7 and 8, next to Cyllage City. }} '''Connecting Cave''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Kalos]]. It initially has 100 tiles arranged in a 10x10 square, including 10 chest tiles, 23 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile. Wild Encounters have 6,503,370 HP.
